<emphasis bold="true" box="[140,650,166,193]" pageId="5" pageNumber="22">
Key to the genera of Indo-Pacific 
<taxonomicName authority="Dana, 1852" box="[540,650,166,192]" class="Malacostraca" family="Serolidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Isopoda" pageId="5" pageNumber="22" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="family">Serolidae</taxonomicName>
